<p><strong>Proof layer in practice:</strong> Taste reviews, freshness testimonials, and unboxing photos in browse and gift-set consideration. For food and beverage brands, Gift set browse includes taste review quotes. Review request delivery +3 days for ambient, +1 day check-in for perishable quality. The failure mode to watch: No proof on gift consideration — default to discounting premium baskets. Monthly operator test: Gift set conversion with taste UGC module vs without.</p>
<p><strong>Analytics layer in practice:</strong> Margin after shipping promos, replenishment conversion, subscription retention, launch sell-through, waste/return proxy via support tags. For food and beverage brands, Weekly margin on email orders including shipping subsidy. Cohort replenishment by consumption segment. The failure mode to watch: Free shipping promo drives revenue negative on heavy cold-chain orders. Monthly operator test: Finance margin line includes shipping subsidy impact monthly.</p>
<p><strong>Deploying the Consumable DTC scenario:</strong> Privy consumption quiz → Sequenzy SKU-timed replenishment → Recharge sync → shipping cutoff modules → Omnisend launch SMS for limited flavors. Document trigger, delay, branch, and suppression rows before launch. Reconcile Shopify net sales weekly — platform attribution will overstate if popup, cart, and SMS discounts stack on the same session.</p>
