<h2>Quarterly stack audit for food and beverage brands</h2>
<p><strong>Week 1 review:</strong> Map SKU consumption windows. Audit Recharge suppressions. List allergen/dietary segmentation gaps. Confirm collision calendar updated for upcoming peak weeks and that subscription, wholesale, or gift-buyer tags still suppress conflicting promos.</p>
