<p><strong>Week 6 review:</strong> Flavor launch waitlist → fulfillment sequence. Omnisend SMS opt-in branch. Confirm collision calendar updated for upcoming peak weeks and that subscription, wholesale, or gift-buyer tags still suppress conflicting promos.</p>
